Class Msdmsnewdocsearch

  • java.lang.Object
    • BaseFormProcessor
      • com.metricstream.systemi.client.servlet.servant.Msdmsnewdocsearch
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DMSConstants

    public class Msdmsnewdocsearch
extends BaseFormProcessor
implements DMSConstants
    This class displays search results on a set of documents. The input for example can be a search for a particular text in all document attachments in the attachment folder.
